  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t瓦房店国土鳖了一辈子总算是整点优雅的东西了（虽然还是瓦房店版的），近期国家大剧院上演法国浪漫主义作曲家德利布的歌剧《拉克美》。官老爷对此显然十分得意，还邀请了几个驻华领馆的“洋大人”出席观剧，并在媒体上宣传此事。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n没想到的是，因该歌剧剧情带有印度少女爱上英国殖民军官的情节，瞬间唤起了洼地的无产阶级韭菜们的自卑感，纷纷对号入座，觉得自己受到了洋人的歧视（我都没看出哪歧视了），评论区如丧考妣。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n更抽象的是，洼地韭菜们此时纷纷与他们原本瞧不起甚至敌视的“印度阿三”共情，怒斥西方白人文化侵略还看不起黄种人（剧中人物都是婆罗门，纯纯的雅利安人，小黄人还嗯蹭），痛批官老爷谄媚洋大人。印度人还没反对这部剧而洼人先坐不住了。<br/>\n<br/>\r\nPS：据官方称，这场歌剧是为了庆祝洼地与阿曼建交而与阿曼的歌剧院合作的。粉红再如此妄议诋毁下去恐怕真会招铁拳。可见粉红的政治智商属实负数，连主子的朋友圈都敢撬。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmMxODBlYmUxMTY2NTM0ZTk2YzFlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xMjAz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc180ebe1166534e96c1e.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1203\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc180ebe1166534e96c1e.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1203\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc180ebe1166534e96c1e.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1203\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWQxNTc3OWJhM2M5YTBlNjc5NjNkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNzE0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad15779ba3c9a0e67963d.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1714\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad15779ba3c9a0e67963d.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1714\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad15779ba3c9a0e67963d.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1714\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTUwODYwMjdmNjJiYmNmYzc5Y2EzLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNjAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e5086027f62bbcfc79ca3.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1600\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e5086027f62bbcfc79ca3.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e5086027f62bbcfc79ca3.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1600\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzIwOWNhNTI4N2M3MjI4NTQ2YTk4LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNTU4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c209ca5287c7228546a98.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1558\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c209ca5287c7228546a98.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1558\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c209ca5287c7228546a98.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1558\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTUwNzgxNzc2MDk3NTEzZmMzYThhLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNDE1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/950781776097513fc3a8a.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1415\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/950781776097513fc3a8a.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1415\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/950781776097513fc3a8a.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1415\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
